0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持百度网盘、阿里云盘、中国移动云盘、天翼云盘、迅雷云盘、夸克网盘、UC 网盘和 123 云等多个平台</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于公开 API 接口实现直链获取，不涉及破解限速功能</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供美化的用户界面和丰富的下载管理功能，如 AB Download Manager 集成及 Aria2 推送支持</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">持续更新以适配各个平台的新版本和修复相关 Bug，提高稳定性与兼容性</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持多服务配置切换，优化脚本执行效率并增强用户体验</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">get-convex/chef</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/get-convex/chef\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/get-convex/chef</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">3.5k</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">Apache-2.0</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">chef 是一个基于 AI 的全栈应用构建工具，专注于后端开发能力。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">内置数据库支持，简化数据管理</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">零配置认证系统，方便用户身份验证</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持文件上传和实时用户界面交互</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">集成后台工作流，实现复杂业务逻辑自动化</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weig